PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the PETER BALLANTYNE CREE NATION BAND, of certain land in Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included, as follows: (a) some 93 hectares as Nemekus Sakahikan Indian Reserve No. 221, (b) some 406 hectares as Sokatisewin Sakahikan Indian Reserve No. 224, and (c) some 2,124 hectares, as Kipahigan Sakahikan Indian Reserve No. 222.
